<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/3281.The_Mind_and_the_Brain"><img alt="The Mind and the Brain: Neuroplasticity and the Power of Mental Force" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1386925436l/3281._SX98_.jpg" />
